/target
# Cargo.lock IS committed: this workspace ships binaries/bindings (adriane-cli,
# bindings/napi, py-bindings) and the release builds with `--locked` for
# reproducibility. A tracked lockfile is required for clean-checkout CI.
*.node
# napi-rs regenerates a JS loader + d.ts on every `napi build`; we ship the
# hand-written bindings/index.js + index.d.ts instead, so the generated ones
# are throwaway.
bindings/napi-generated.*
